description:
					This charming villa is the ideal family home or second residence by the sea. The villa on a plot of 697 m2 is tucked away in a dead end in a quiet residential area just 5 min from Knokke. This detached villa offers with spacious garden and sunny south facing terrace, 3 bedrooms and an indoor garage and 160 m² habitable surface many assets to create your dream home.

Layout: on the ground floor there is a spacious entrance hall with cloakroom and toilet, a spacious living room with parquet and all around access to the terrace and the garden, a fully equipped kitchen and an indoor garage. On the first floor there are 3 bedrooms and bathroom with bath and shower and a spacious night hall. There is the possibility of extension to the back.

The main assets are:
* Very spacious villa with 160 m² of living space;
* 3 bedrooms;
* Spacious and sunny living room with access to sunny garden;
* Classically designed property located in quiet residential area in a dead end street 5 minutes from the beach;
* Good location in relation to the roads;
* Expansion to the rear possible;
